ðŸ”¹ Step 1: Choose and Install a Tool

You can use OpenVAS (Greenbone Community Edition) or Nessus Essentials (both are free).

For beginners, Nessus Essentials is easier.
ðŸ‘‰ Download: https://www.tenable.com/products/nessus/nessus-essentials
