## Findings:
1. OpenSSH 7.2 outdated (High) â†’ Fix: Upgrade to latest OpenSSH  
2. SSL/TLS weak cipher detected (Medium) â†’ Fix: Disable weak ciphers  
3. Missing Windows Security Update KBxxxx (Critical) â†’ Fix: Update OS  

## Screenshots:
[Insert screenshots of Nessus/OpenVAS results]

## Conclusion:
